The paper deals with the problem of presentation attack detection in fingerprint biometric systems, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The proposed technique involves image representation and feature extraction, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of different sensors, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
